  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    LoginActivity
    An activity class for the Login Screen, used to handle logic so the user can enter their login information and attempt to login.
    MatchesScreen
    The screen used to display the restaurants the user has been matched with
    SignUpActivity
    The Sign-Up screen; The user can enter their account information here and request to sign-up to Dinder
    SocialActivity
    The Social Screen displays the user's friends list, allows the user to invite friends to their group, and allows the user to send friend requests to other users.
    UserHomeActivity
    The Home Screen is considered the default location of the app.
    UserProfileActivity
    The User Profile screen, used to display the user's information and allow them to modify their dietary preferences and other settings affecting the rest of the app.
